Join us at the Nickerson Gardens: ROSS Program Job & Resource Fair!
Come connect with job opportunities, community resources, and support services—all in one place!

Date: May 9, 2025
Time: 1 PM – 4 PM
Location: Nickerson Gardens Gym
11251 Compton Ave, Los Angeles, CA 90059

Enjoy:
	•	Free food
	•	DJ & raffles
	•	Gift card giveaways
	•	Special resources for pregnant moms & parents with young children (0–5 yrs)

Don’t miss out—bring a friend!
Questions? Email: tiffany.mansour@hacla.org or call (323) 567-2974
